Krishna District SC Corporation Executive Director N.V.V. Satyanarayana has invited applications from eligible women beneficiaries of the governmentâ€™s new land purchase scheme.Mr. Satyanarayana on Saturday told the media that the government would sanction maximum subsidy of Rs. 3 lakh, apart from helping grant of loan worth another Rs. 2 lakh from the Srinidhi Credit Co-operative Federation to purchase land under the scheme. The district-level committee will finalise the list of beneficiaries belonging to SC community and one should belong to the category of Below Poverty Line, added Mr. Satyanarayana.